maneuver.instruction: Drive north.
Turn left onto Santoshi Mata Road.
Turn right onto Agra Road.
Enter Chatrapati Shivaji Maharaj Putala Chowk and take the 2nd exit onto NH61/Kalyan-Bhiwandi Road.
Turn left onto NH848/AH47/Mumbai Agra National Highway.
Take the exit.
Turn left onto Lal Bahadur Shastri Marg.
Keep right to stay on Lal Bahadur Shastri Marg.
Bear left onto Meenatai Thakrey Flyover.
Keep right to stay on Meenatai Thakrey Flyover.
Stay straight to take the ramp.
Make a right U-turn at Lazarus rd to stay on Lal Bahadur Shastri Marg.
Take the exit.
Your destination is on the left.
